title: ASC Trarza Nadi Sporting
text:
ASC Trarza Nadi Sporting is a <a href="Mauritania">Mauritanean</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Rosso">Rosso</a>, the capital of the <a href="Trarza">Trarza</a> region. 
The club plays in the <a href="Mauritanean%20Premier%20League">Mauritanean Premier League</a>.
Stadium.
Currently the team plays at the 1000 capacity <a href="Stade%20Trarza">Stade Trarza</a>.
